{"tid":2436852,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【DSE Chem】高質 Mock 延長截卷喇","createTime":"2021-03-07T12:37:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T16:30:47.000Z","uid":257543,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7bda9a5805ff80506f6427c13aad7d26cc221db5","tid":2436852,"uid":257543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T12:37:48.000Z","msg":"DSE 就嚟到，努力溫緊書嘅大家難免會緊張。呢一年武肺搞到停課，又搞到好多 Mock 都開唔成，相信大家一定為住唔夠應試經驗而不知所措。<br />\n<br />\n唔使驚！你問我答 Chem 團隊嚟緊就會推出 2021 年嘅 Mock 卷，包括 <strong><span class=\"green\">P1 同 P2 全卷，擬卷過程經過專業人士仔細監督，確保無出錯題，而且模式、題型都貼近 DSE</span></strong>，絕對可以幫大家提早作準備，同埋大概知道自己嘅能力～<br />\n<br />\n最緊要嘅係，呢個 Mock 係為咗支持各位同路人，只要大家嘅踴躍參與同幫到大家喺 DSE 到攞到理想嘅成績就係對你問我答 Chem 團隊最好嘅回報～<br />\n<br />\n我哋出 mock 嘅初心都係想幫到各位為住 dse、為住理想而晝夜奮鬥嘅同學仔，所以我哋為咗令更加多同學仔可以有時間做到份 mock，我哋決定延長做卷時間：<br />\n<br />\n截卷日期順延 6 天，即係 <strong><span class=\"x-large\"><ins><span class=\"red\">3 月 13 號 23 時 59 分先截止。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎入 group 攞卷：👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻 <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/DSEChem2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDSEChem2020&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bKtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=90038468\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/DSEChem2020</a></span></ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>不成功不收費，成功都不收費。</strong>期望可以幫到大家。"},{"pid":"7dc970639e0710b7bc9f2962b86d2247ff4c8d7a","tid":2436852,"uid":257543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:07:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64aa92782af430ed0d3b6ea6cf8e706a30e4002f","tid":2436852,"uid":257543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:59:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa56b7860897c879cd8113a6f8cb8ba33e6397a9","tid":2436852,"uid":321580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T14:26:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a674bfe2f0c4e73856e1025f8928991672ca3882","tid":2436852,"uid":257543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa56b7860897c879cd8113a6f8cb8ba33e6397a9","tid":2436852,"uid":321580,"like":1,"disli